{"tid":1264786,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【Nintendo Switch】任天堂正考慮拓展會免陣容 FC外還會有N64、NGC遊戲","createTime":"2019-06-29T00:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T14:38:38.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00fedbd259e7b8814cab4cb5adaa6fb05f882dc1","tid":1264786,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T00:14:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368800330057141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2368800330057141&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6swCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=074beec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2368800330057141</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xuuZ9Ud.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxuuZ9Ud.png&h=88b4aeec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【NS】任天堂正考慮拓展會免陣容 FC外還會有N64、NGC遊戲<br />\n<br />\n  在最近的股東大會上，社長古川俊太郎在被問到是否有復刻N64或是NGC的打算時，雖然表示硬件部分沒法透露更多信息，但是正在考慮通過擴展Switch Online會員專享的遊戲庫陣容（目前只提供FC遊戲），以及其他可行的方式來提供相關遊戲軟件。 &ldquo;我們也意識到，現在有不少觀點表示想要玩一些過去的老遊戲&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  當問及NS的新機型相關問題時，古川並不打算回答&ldquo;我們已經知道現在有很多相關報導，但是如果我們隊傳聞和推測進行回應的話，毫無疑問會從我們的消費者那裡偷走那些'驚喜'，並且這也是對我們所有股東的利益有損的，所以我們不打算作相關回答。&rdquo;不過他也表示&ldquo;一般來說，我們永遠都在研究新硬件。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Qzb00T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Qzb00T.png&h=35dbf10a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e997d39006982f803edb53a5988b243fafafde6","tid":1264786,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f74c3f1189370d21c0c61b7d8fad0a9b1f290f9","tid":1264786,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1743b0acda479af836e1f1cb9c542b6eabf26a3b","tid":126478